text:
Avatar
Display a user or entity representation as image, icon, or text initials.
{"requires":["alt text for accessibility"],"allows":["image src","icon element","text initials via alt"],"forbids":["interactive content within avatar"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"image","useWhen":["user has a profile photo"]},{"name":"icon","useWhen":["generic entity or placeholder representation"]},{"name":"text","useWhen":["no image available, display initials"]}]}

BottomNavigation
App-level bottom navigation bar. Accepts 2–5 <BottomNavItem> children with a shared `labelType` (none / 1line / 2line). Supports controlled or uncontrolled active value, multi-accent appearance roles, and an optional top hairline divider.
{"requires":["children"],"allows":[],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"1line","useWhen":["1 Line"]},{"name":"2line","useWhen":["2 Lines"]},{"name":"none","useWhen":["None"]}]}

Checkbox
Binary selection control for forms and settings with tri-state (indeterminate) support.
{"requires":["label or aria-label"],"allows":["indeterminate state","read-only mode"],"forbids":["use as a toggle for non-boolean values"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"default","useWhen":["standard form checkbox"]},{"name":"indeterminate","useWhen":["parent of partially-selected group"]},{"name":"readOnly","useWhen":["display-only state, value visible but not editable"]}]}

CheckboxField
`Field.Root` + **Checkbox** with integrated `Field.Label` / `Field.Description`, optional `infoIconSlot`, `error` / `feedback`, native `Field.Error` slot, and optional `InputDynamicText` row — same composition contract as **InputField** (Figma `.DNA/InputField` stack; control DNA from Checkbox). Colour follows `appearance` on the inner Checkbox.
{"requires":[],"allows":["feedback","dynamicTextSlot","infoIconSlot"],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"checked","useWhen":["Checked"]},{"name":"unchecked","useWhen":["Unchecked"]}]}

CircularProgressIndicator
Circular progress arc. Determinate variant renders an arc proportional to `value`; indeterminate renders a spinning animation. Optional center content (icon or auto percentage). 10 t-shirt sizes. Multi-accent appearance roles.
{"requires":[],"allows":[],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"determinate","useWhen":["Determinate"]},{"name":"indeterminate","useWhen":["Indeterminate"]}]}

Container
Page-level width container. `fluid` grows with the viewport (default). `fixed` caps at --Grid-MaxWidth per platform and centers. `full-bleed` is edge-to-edge for hero sections and full-width media.
{"requires":[],"allows":[],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"fluid","useWhen":["Fluid"]},{"name":"fixed","useWhen":["Fixed"]},{"name":"full-bleed","useWhen":["Full bleed"]}]}

Divider
Visual separator between sections, list items, or content groups.
{"requires":["orientation context"],"allows":["label or icon slot","round caps"],"forbids":["interactive content","non-separator use"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"low attention","useWhen":["subtle content separation (default)"]},{"name":"medium attention","useWhen":["prominent section boundary"]},{"name":"high attention","useWhen":["strong separator between major sections"]}]}

Icon
Render a semantic or custom icon with configurable size, colour role, and emphasis level.
{"requires":["icon prop (semantic name or React element)"],"allows":["aria-label for non-decorative use"],"forbids":["interactive behaviour (use IconButton instead)","text content"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"high emphasis","useWhen":["primary content icon requiring strongest contrast"]},{"name":"medium emphasis","useWhen":["secondary or supporting icon"]},{"name":"low emphasis","useWhen":["subtle decorative icon"]}]}

IconContained
Display an icon within a filled container shape with attention-level emphasis.
{"requires":["icon prop (semantic name or React element)"],"allows":["aria-label for accessibility"],"forbids":["interactive behaviour (non-interactive display only)","text content"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"high attention","useWhen":["prominent solid bold fill container"]},{"name":"medium attention","useWhen":["subtle tinted fill container"]}]}

Image
Display an image with aspect ratio presets, loading states, and optional interactive overlay.
{"requires":["src (required)","alt text (required)"],"allows":["aspect ratio preset","interactive mode with click handler","custom fallback on error"],"forbids":["decorative images without alt=\"\"","interactive mode without aria-label"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"static","useWhen":["display-only image content"]},{"name":"interactive","useWhen":["clickable image with state layer and focus ring"]}]}

IndicatorBadge
Non-interactive status/presence indicator dot. Supports multi-accent appearance roles and five sizes.
{"requires":[],"allows":[],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"bold","useWhen":["Default"]}]}

Input
Low-level single-line text entry control. Use standalone only when you do not need a visible label, helper text, or validation chrome; otherwise compose it inside InputField.
{"requires":["an accessible name — aria-label when standalone, or a Field.Label via InputField"],"allows":["start adornment (icon/affix)","end adornment (icon/affix/clear button)"],"forbids":["multi-line content (use a textarea pattern)","using errorHighlight standalone — use InputField for validation UX"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"default (medium)","useWhen":["standard outlined input on a default surface"]},{"name":"high attention","useWhen":["filled neutral background is wanted for emphasis"]}]}

InputField
Text input field: `Field.Root` + **Input** (`Field.Label` / `Field.Description` for label-stack copy, `Field.Control` for the `<input>`, 4-slot shell), then `InputFeedback` (including native `Field.Error` when there is no string `error` / custom `feedback`), and DynamicText. Default info uses `IconButton` + `Tooltip` (override with `infoIconSlot`). Optional `labelSlot` replaces string `label` / `description`.
{"requires":[],"allows":["labelSlot","start","start2","end","end2","feedback","dynamicTextSlot","dynamicText","helperButton"],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"default","useWhen":["Default"]}]}

Modal
Focused overlay with structured header/body/footer layout and scroll management. The modal popup is role-neutral; per-role styling is applied to the slot children (footer buttons, headerStart, body content).
{"requires":[],"allows":["headerStart","children","footerStart","footerEnd"],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"S","useWhen":["Small"]},{"name":"M","useWhen":["Medium"]},{"name":"L","useWhen":["Large"]},{"name":"FullWidth","useWhen":["Full Width"]}]}

PaginationDots
Windowed pagination indicator for carousels and multi-page content. Shows a fixed window of dots that scroll with the active index. Edge dots shrink to signal more content on either side. Supports loop (infinite) and non-loop (end-grow) modes. Fully accessible: roving tabindex, keyboard nav, aria-selected.
{"requires":[],"allows":[],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"non-loop","useWhen":["Non-loop"]},{"name":"loop","useWhen":["Loop"]}]}

Radio
Single-selection control within a mutually-exclusive option group.
{"requires":["value prop","RadioGroup parent","label or aria-label"],"allows":["read-only mode","group-level appearance inheritance"],"forbids":["standalone use without RadioGroup","multiple selection"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"default","useWhen":["standard option in a radio group"]},{"name":"readOnly","useWhen":["display-only, value shown but cannot change"]}]}

RadioField
`Field.Root` + **RadioGroup** with optional `Field.Label` / `Field.Description`, `infoIconSlot`, `error` / `feedback`, native `Field.Error` slot, and optional `InputDynamicText` row — same shell as **InputField** / **CheckboxField**. Integrated single mode has no `Radio` children; colour follows **`appearance`** on inner radios.
{"requires":[],"allows":["children","feedback","dynamicTextSlot","infoIconSlot"],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"default","useWhen":["Default"]}]}

SelectableButton
Toggle button with text label and optional start/end slots for binary selection within groups.
{"requires":["children (text label) or aria-label"],"allows":["start/end slots (icon, badge)","contained/uncontained mode","condensed mode","fullWidth"],"forbids":["use for navigation (use Button instead)","nested interactive elements"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"high attention","useWhen":["selected state needs bold fill emphasis"]},{"name":"medium attention","useWhen":["selected state with subtle tinted fill"]},{"name":"low attention","useWhen":["selected state with ghost appearance and accent border"]}]}

SelectableIconButton
Icon-only toggle button for compact binary selection with configurable shape layout.
{"requires":["icon prop","aria-label (required — icon-only)"],"allows":["condensed mode","3:2 layout variant","loading state"],"forbids":["text content (use SelectableButton instead)","missing aria-label"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"high attention","useWhen":["selected state needs bold fill emphasis"]},{"name":"medium attention","useWhen":["selected state with subtle tinted fill"]},{"name":"low attention","useWhen":["selected state with ghost appearance and accent border"]}]}

SelectableSingleTextButton
Text-only toggle button for binary selection — no start/end slots, simpler than SelectableButton.
{"requires":["children (text label — required)"],"allows":["condensed mode","fullWidth","loading state"],"forbids":["icon slots (use SelectableButton instead)","missing text content"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"high attention","useWhen":["selected state needs bold fill emphasis"]},{"name":"medium attention","useWhen":["selected state with subtle tinted fill"]},{"name":"low attention","useWhen":["selected state with ghost appearance and accent border"]}]}

SingleTextButton
Circular single-text action button (max 2 characters, e.g. "Ag", "En"). Attention level drives the visual: high=bold fill, medium=subtle fill, low=ghost. 3 sizes (S/M/L). Shape customisable per brand.
{"requires":[],"allows":[],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"high","useWhen":["High"]},{"name":"medium","useWhen":["Medium"]},{"name":"low","useWhen":["Low"]}]}

Slider
Precision range input. Multi-accent appearance, inside/outside knob styles, optional step ticks, and a value tooltip that follows the thumb.
{"requires":[],"allows":["start","end"],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"continuous","useWhen":["Continuous"]},{"name":"range","useWhen":["Range"]}]}

Stepper
Numeric input control with increment and decrement buttons for bounded integer values.
{"requires":["numeric value context"],"allows":["min/max constraints","custom step","shift multiplier","error state"],"forbids":["non-numeric values","string entry"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"high","useWhen":["primary quantity input requiring high emphasis"]},{"name":"medium","useWhen":["default quantity field (most common use)"]},{"name":"low","useWhen":["de-emphasised numeric control"]}]}

Surface
Container primitive that opts descendants into the OneUI surface cascade via [data-surface]. The `mode` prop maps to one of the 7 canonical surface tokens (default/ghost/minimal/subtle/moderate/bold/elevated). Optional transparent material composites over arbitrary media.
{"requires":[],"allows":[],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"default","useWhen":["Default"]},{"name":"ghost","useWhen":["Ghost"]},{"name":"minimal","useWhen":["Minimal"]},{"name":"subtle","useWhen":["Subtle"]},{"name":"moderate","useWhen":["Moderate"]},{"name":"bold","useWhen":["Bold"]},{"name":"elevated","useWhen":["Elevated"]}]}

Switch
Immediate binary toggle — state takes effect on change without a submit action.
{"requires":["label or aria-label"],"allows":["read-only mode","accent override"],"forbids":["use in forms requiring explicit submit","replace with Checkbox for non-immediate effects"]}
{"rules":[{"name":"default","useWhen":["immediate on/off setting"]},{"name":"readOnly","useWhen":["display-only permission or system setting"]}]}

Tabs
Accessible tabbed navigation. Uses Base UI Tabs primitive for keyboard navigation, arrow/Home/End keys, and automatic focus management. Three sizes (S/M/L), two orientations (horizontal/vertical). Matching Figma spec: selected tab gets an animated tinted indicator, tinted-accessible label color, and a surface-aware double-ring focus halo. Supports start + end content slots; icon + badge are legacy aliases.
{"requires":[],"allows":["start","end"],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"horizontal","useWhen":["Horizontal"]},{"name":"vertical","useWhen":["Vertical"]}]}

Text
Inline / block text. Six typography roles with role-specific size scales, canonical multi-accent appearance, attention levels, italic / underline / strikethrough, latin / multi-script font fallback, and line-clamp truncation. Defaults to `span`; set `as` for headings or anchors. When using the `text` prop with the `link` slot, avoid `aria-hidden` on the root unless the link is decorative — the slot remains focusable.
{"requires":[],"allows":["link"],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"display","useWhen":["Display"]},{"name":"headline","useWhen":["Headline"]},{"name":"title","useWhen":["Title"]},{"name":"body","useWhen":["Body"]},{"name":"label","useWhen":["Label"]},{"name":"code","useWhen":["Code"]}]}

Tooltip
Floating hover / focus label that attaches to a trigger element. Supports the Figma position alias (top/topStart/topEnd/...), Base UI side+align, controlled/uncontrolled open state, arrow, portal, and configurable delay.
{"requires":["children","content"],"allows":[],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"default","useWhen":["Default"]}]}

TouchSlider
Chunky fingertip-friendly slider. The track is the tap target; the fill represents the value. Ideal for touch devices, TV remotes, and large-target contexts.
{"requires":[],"allows":["start","end"],"forbids":[]}
{"rules":[{"name":"rounded","useWhen":["Rounded"]},{"name":"sharp","useWhen":["Sharp"]}]}
